Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:08.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Your teacher comes back today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.41,0:00:09.16,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.45,0:00:12.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see. Then I'd better say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.58,0:00:14.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Should we leave a little earlier than usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:15.67,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.51,0:00:25.68,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:29.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:32.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's get a move on, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.93,0:00:34.52,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.52,0:00:37.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio, say "I'm going" to Mommy. {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:40.90,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:44.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.83,0:00:56.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, Ushio! {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:00:58.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's dangerous, so wait! {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.25,0:01:00.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:34.80,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Stew!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:37.22,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Stew!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:38.01,Default,Bot,0,0,0,,Gof! Gof!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:39.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.97,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,The kindergarten pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:43.43,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:45.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why a boar?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, it can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.69,0:02:51.56,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You must be Okazaki Ushio-chan's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:58.49,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I'm Ushio-chan's teacher, Fujibayashi Kyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:01.28,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:05.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes, the pleasure is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:14.71,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've ever seen a face like that on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:20.09,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You should have known the moment you saw Botan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:23.47,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Or have you forgotten about me already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:26.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So that is Botan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:26.89,Default,Bot,0,0,0,,Gof!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:33.82,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Ushio-chan, to tell you the truth,\Nyour daddy and I went to school together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:37.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She was violent back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She always bullied me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:43.41,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't make stories up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:45.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She was also a good friend of Mommy's.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:47.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:04:00.34,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Sanae-san came and said that you'd eventually come\Nso not to tell the whole story until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:04.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see... Sanae-san did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:08.52,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(957.273,415.8)}Episode 20
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:08.52,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(960,712.5)}Capriccio of Days with Ushio
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:11.23,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Fate is pretty strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:14.73,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Whoever thought I'd be Ushio-chan's teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:17.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I must have made you worry a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:18.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.78,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,It must have been hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:25.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:30.12,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Ryou, Kotomi, and Youhei are all worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:36.29,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,We were thinking maybe we should visit you when we got together over New Years, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.96,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,We ended up saying it'd be best to leave you alone for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:40.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:46.47,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,But this means that everything's settled, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:47.56,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,All the loose ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:49.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:51.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How's Ushio doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:53.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is she getting along with everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.11,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,She's a really good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:58.69,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,She's not cynical like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:02.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I bet she got it from her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:06.49,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,But I'd say she's more active than her mother was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:11.87,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,She runs off on her own when I take my eyes off her, so I'm extra careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:13.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:14.83,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:17.29,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:18.00,Default-alt,Kid,0,0,0,,Good morning, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.46,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Good morning, Takuya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll get going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:24.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll leave Ushio with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:27.26,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,If anything happens, call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:29.31,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I'll help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:32.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll be relying on you, Fujibayashi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:37.36,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Ushio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:39.65,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Your daddy's heading to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:45.61,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Have a good day, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, off I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:56.33,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad that you can live with your daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:57.63,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:01.34,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,All right, shall we go inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:02.05,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:05.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Fuko-chan is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:08.97,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Yeah. She wants to visit your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:12.10,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Do you have any plans this coming Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:14.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:15.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:19.23,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Apparently she wants to become friends with Ushio-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:21.94,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,It'd help if you would let her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:27.45,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Fuko-chan just got out of hospital and needs to practice walking on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:30.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. She's going through rehab.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:33.41,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,She's also shy around people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:36.75,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,It's rare that she actively wants to meet someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:39.71,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,I want to create such opportunities for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:45.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It looks like Ushio likes Fuko-chan, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:47.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We'll be expecting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.43,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:50.55,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,And thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:52.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:06.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Ushio. You're going to have a guest tomorrow. {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:08.55,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:10.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ibuki Fuko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:11.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You remember her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:13.93,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:17.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She said she wants to play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:18.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.56,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup. I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're happy about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:24.61,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup. I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:32.20,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Daddy. Can you sing Mommy's song?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:35.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Again? You really like it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:38.33,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup. It's my favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:43.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right. But it's nighttime, so quietly, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:51.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Dango, dango, dango, dango...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:54.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A great big dango family!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:09:05.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,4000)}A mischievous roasted dango, a kind, sweet bean dango...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:18.97,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuko's here for a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:21.85,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Thank you for having Fuko over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:27.90,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Now, right off the bat, Ushio-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:30.27,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Be Fuko's little sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:31.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, she won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:36.65,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuko isn't talking to you. Fuko's talking with Ushio-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:40.70,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Ushio-chan. Don't you like Fuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:43.74,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:45.33,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:48.87,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,But I'm staying with Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:50.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:56.05,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Then Fuko will spend today to win you over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:59.80,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,First, this is the gift for us getting to know each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:03.68,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,It's a made-to-order bread by Furukawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:06.06,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Will you eat it, Ushio-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:09.19,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:12.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's a pretty cute design coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:14.82,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Itadakimasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:20.57,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:25.33,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Cute Ushio-chan is eating cute bread, and her cuteness just doubled!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:27.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't hug her for every reason you make up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:32.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We're having lunch now. Do you want to eat with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:37.59,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Are you trying to win Fuko over?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:38.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:43.60,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuko heard that you lost your wife, Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:44.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:48.81,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,It's no surprise that you see a sliver of her in Fuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:51.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.15,0:11:53.02,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:57.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa doesn't resemble you at all; almost like a separate species.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:00.40,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,You had an alien as your wife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:01.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm saying you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.74,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuko's not an alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:06.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I can't follow your thought process.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:10.96,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuko has an average Earthling's thought process.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:14.88,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Neighbors often say that Fuko is a very average Earthling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:16.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What kind of neighbors do you have?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:19.55,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Therefore, let's go home together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That doesn't follow at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:27.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,{\fs75.6}Besides, if you represent the average Earthling's thought process, the world would be gone in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:30.35,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuko cannot understand your statement at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:35.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What would you do if there's a button in front of you that says "don't press"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:37.94,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuko will hide and press it secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:40.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That was the launch button of a nuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:44.32,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,That was not fair! You tricked Fuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:47.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The Earth would be gone in less than three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:49.83,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Then here's a question for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:56.38,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,What would you do if tights that say\N"don't wear" were lying on the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:58.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'd leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:13:03.30,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,You're lying! Fuko's sure that, not being able to control yourself, you'd put them on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:06.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okazaki's the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:13.27,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,The world would end because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:20.11,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,It's late now, but you didn't add any sleeping pills, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:25.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Even if you were sleeping your butt off, I wouldn't touch you with a six-foot pole, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:31.54,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,D-Does that mean you care about Fuko that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Heck no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:34.83,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,You don't have to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:35.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Who says?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:37.29,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:38.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:40.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Enough! I won't talk with you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:42.05,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Are you embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.14,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,And so, let's play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:50.68,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Ushio-chan, do you know how to play blackjack or gin rummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:53.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey. You're talking to a five-year old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:14:00.61,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Sorry. Fuko's an adult,\Nso Fuko suggested advanced games.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:04.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you know any games, Ushio? {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.45,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Sevens!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:11.70,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Ushio-chan, best choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:13.66,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,That is an addictive game!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:15.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're such a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:20.09,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san. You're holding on to the ten of hearts, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:23.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Well, since I still have lots of card I can play.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:26.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're up, Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:27.80,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:29.97,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,That was great, Ushio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:32.60,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Now Fuko's back in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:35.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Dang, when I had her cornered in well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:40.65,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Just from that one move, we can tell that Ushio-chan loves Fuko more than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:41.73,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:43.32,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,In your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:51.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you were alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:03.92,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san. Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:09.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry. It was my turn, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:15.60,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,So you do see a sliver of your wife in Fuko after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I said that wouldn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:20.10,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Perhaps our personalities are different?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:23.15,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Maybe your wife was a childish person?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:26.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I can't name a person more childish than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:30.57,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,You've never met your mother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:33.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Right. She only knows her face from pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:37.37,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,But I heard stories from Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:41.75,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,What kind of person was your Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:43.71,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.92,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,A big crybaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:51.93,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,But a person who did her best to give birth to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:57.43,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,And, the person Daddy really loved!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:05.86,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:10.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She just comes back to me at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:15.49,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuko has free time, so call whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:19.29,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuko will come whenever you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:21.75,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuko will do whatever Fuko can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:25.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you trying to be nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:30.42,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,It's not like that; Fuko just wants to play with Ushio-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:32.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:35.93,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuko will be heading home now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:37.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Just say bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:40.39,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Let's go, Ushio-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:42.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:47.90,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Oh well. There will be plenty of opportunities in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:51.03,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Be careful when you go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:54.03,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuko will say hi when Fuko sees you on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:59.58,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuko has memorized Ushio-chan's scent, so Fuko can tell when she's nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:00.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you an animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:03.46,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,When it happens, let's play together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:04.63,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:11.84,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:13.59,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup. Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:19.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:21.23,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,She was funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:23.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's very true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:27.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's clean up and take a bath, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:27.90,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:42.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Botan doesn't get angry over that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:45.92,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I think she takes it as a back rub and likes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:45.92,Default-alt,Bot,0,0,0,,Gof, gof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:50.67,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Ushio-chan! Good-for-nothing's here for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:54.84,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:55.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry I made you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:59.14,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Wow, you totally have the doting parent look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:02.98,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Ushio-chan, what should we do with your pathetic daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:05.89,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Daddy's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:09.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She has good eyes for spotting men.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:17.53,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I gave Ushio-chan a handout for\Nthe sports day, so read it, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:18.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sports day?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:23.62,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Yeah. There are family events, too,\Nso you'd better practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:27.62,San,San,0,0,0,,I knew about the sports day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:31.13,San,San,0,0,0,,The head of the neighborhood committee told me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:33.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then will you come cheer for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:34.63,San,San,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:36.93,San,San,0,0,0,,But rather than cheering...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:40.05,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Akki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.14,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey Ushio. Didn't know you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:44.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's with that outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:48.60,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Jogging in preparation for the sports day, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:51.40,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I can't stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:52.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's not in the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:19:01.83,San,San,0,0,0,,{\fs70.2}Akio-san is a fast runner, so he was asked to run anchor for the teachers in place of the principal, who has a bad waist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:04.49,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You'll be on the parent team, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:06.08,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It's a showdown between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:08.75,San,San,0,0,0,,That's a very exciting situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hold on one minute please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:12.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I haven't decided to be in the relay yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:16.63,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Sanae, tell the principal he'll run anchor for the parent team.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:17.80,San,San,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:19.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,They're so forceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:21.01,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:23.39,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:29.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right! Daddy's gonna do his best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:30.52,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Do his best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:34.36,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:38.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I can't look pathetic when my daughter's watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:57.13,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Ushio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:00.34,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Fuko Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:04.43,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,So you like to go on strolls?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:05.35,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:08.64,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,You're not scared of getting lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:10.23,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:17.19,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,It's like you don't know which way to go,\Nand you feel unsure, are in trouble, and can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:20.03,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,You're not scared of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:21.36,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:23.07,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,You're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:25.45,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuko should learn that from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:30.50,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,But Fuko thinks it's dangerous for little girls to walk outside alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:33.92,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Ushio-chan, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:43.59,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,It's the new hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:47.35,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Do you like it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:48.10,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:50.56,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:52.19,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Just because.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:55.69,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Just because, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:29.35,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's finally the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:32.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah! The day I show you who's boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:43.32,San,San,0,0,0,,Ushio. We can hardly wait for tomorrow to come, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.91,0:21:48.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ushio?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:52.75,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I couldn't pee alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:21:59.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ushio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:02.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She's burning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:09.74,Continue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(1611.818,859.5)}To be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.74,0:23:43.60,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\pos(981.818,452.25)\c&HFFFFFF&\be2\4c&H000000&\3c&H454845&\bord3.15}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.47,0:23:43.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.02,0:23:48.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,My family might just be getting toyed with by this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.23,0:23:53.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Given happiness, then having it snatched away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.24,0:24:04.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I can't even grant one wish my only daughter has?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.54,0:24:09.80,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(981.818,384.75)\c&HFFFFFF&\be2\4c&H000000&\3c&H454845&\bord3.15}Episode 21
