Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.00,0:24:08.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:33.11,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Namida ga kobore ochiru noha nan no sei
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.94,0:08:44.66,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Kasane sugita toshi no sei
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:57.05,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Isu ni yurarete yume wo mite itanda
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.88,0:09:09.19,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Anata ga chiisana shukufuku no nakade umarete kita hi no
Dialogue: 2,0:09:08.85,0:09:22.32,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Komorebi wo shiawase na hi wo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:33.11,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\be2}What causes my tears to fall?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.94,0:08:44.66,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\be2}It's from living for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:57.05,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,300)}{\be2}I was having a dream, sitting in a rocking chair,
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.88,0:09:09.19,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,200)}{\be2}Of sunlight peaking past branches and of the happy day
Dialogue: 2,0:09:08.85,0:09:22.32,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,750)}{\be2}When you were born surrounded by blessings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:35.60,japro,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Yancha na yaki dango yasashii an dango
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:43.95,japro,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Minna, minna, awasete hyakunin kazoku
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:53.58,japro,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Akachan dango ha itsumo shiawase no naka de
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:11:02.80,japro,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Toshiyori dango ha me wo hosometeru
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:12.85,japro,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Nakayoshi dango te wo tsunagi ookina marui wa ni naruyo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:22.57,japro,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Machi wo tsukuri dango boshi no ue minna de warai auyo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:31.91,japro,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Usagi mo sora de te wo futte miteru dekkai otsuki-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:42.30,japro,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Ureshii koto kanashii koto mo zenbu marumete
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:35.60,japro,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}A mischievous roasted dango, a kind sweet bean dango
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:43.95,japro,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Gather them all up and it{\fnClannad}’{\r}s a family of a hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:53.58,japro,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}A baby dango is always cradled in happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:11:02.80,japro,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}An old dango gazes with squinty eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:12.85,japro,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}The dango friends will all hold hands and form a big circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:22.57,japro,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}They{\fnClannad}’{\r}ll found a village on a dango planet and all smile together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:31.91,japro,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}The rabbits are waving their hands from the big moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:42.30,japro,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Roll up all the happy and sad things...
